data.description: Excellent location for a small acreage.  This 3 bed, 2 bath home with a single attached garage as well as a double detached garage sits on 1.1 acre just 1/4 mile off Highway 30 approximately 10 minutes east of Grand Island.  Wonderful updates throughout!  The roof was new in 2018, and the furnace and air conditioner were replaced in 2019, and serviced in 2021.  A clog-proof beaver system was installed as water proofing of the crawl space in 2021 as well. The seller has a 2.49% VA loan that is transferrable to qualified applicants.
